ActNorthwest Territories Devolution Act
SubjectOrder Fixing April 1, 2014 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing April 1, 2014 as the day on which all of the provisions of Part 1 of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES DEVOLUTION ACT, other than sections 47 and 64; and sections 113, 116, 125 and 126, subsection 128(3), section 130, subsections 132(2) and (4) and 135(1), sections 139 and 140, subsections 141(1) and 142(2), sections 145 and 163, subsections 173(2), 174(1) and 175(3), sections 177, 182 and 185, subsection 187(2), sections 188 and 189, subsection 190(2), sections 192 and 194 to 198 and subsection 213(1), chapter 2 of the Statutes of Canada, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2014-0034 Publication Date: 2014-04-09
